data.title: Brian Wilson
authors: Contributors to The Beach Boys Database Wiki
data.meta_description: Brian Douglas Wilson (Born June 20, 1942) is an American singer, songwriter, music producer and founding member of the Beach Boys. During several periods in their history, including their commercial height in the mid-1960s, Brian served as the group's creative leader and sole producer.
